 class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># 农产品管理系统项目文档</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 1. 项目概述</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">农产品管理系统(NCP-MS)是一个集成化平台，用于管理农产品的生产、库存和销售等全生命周期。系统采用前后端分离架构，提供了直观的用户界面和强大的后台管理功能，旨在提高农产品管理效率，确保农产品质量追溯和供应链可视化。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 1.1 系统架构</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">系统采用前后端分离的微服务架构:</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 前端: Vue.js + Element UI</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 后端: Spring Boot + Spring Cloud</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 数据库: MySQL</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 缓存: Redis</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 1.2 主要功能模块</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品管理: 农产品基础信息管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 生产管理: 农产品种植、收获信息记录与追踪</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 库存管理: 产品入库、出库、库存盘点</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 系统管理: 用户、角色、菜单、权限管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 2. 技术架构</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 2.1 前端技术栈</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- 基础框架: Vue.js 2.x</span><br><span class=\"line\">- UI组件库: Element UI</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 状态管理: Vuex</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 路由管理: Vue Router</span><br><span class=\"line\">- HTTP客户端: Axios</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 构建工具: Webpack</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 2.2 后端技术栈</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- 基础框架: Spring Boot 2.5.x</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 微服务: Spring Cloud</span><br><span class=\"line\">- ORM框架: MyBatis</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 数据库: MySQL 5.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 缓存: Redis</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 权限控制: Spring Security + JWT</span><br><span class=\"line\">- API文档: Swagger</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 日志: Logback</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 2.3 项目结构</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>ncp_ms&#x2F;<br>├── ncp_ms-admin&#x2F;        # 后端入口模块<br>├── ncp_ms-common&#x2F;       # 通用工具模块<br>├── ncp_ms-framework&#x2F;    # 核心框架模块<br>├── ncp_ms-system&#x2F;       # 系统管理模块<br>├── ncp_ms-product&#x2F;      # 产品管理模块<br>├── ncp_ms-produce&#x2F;      # 生产管理模块<br>├── ncp_ms-inventory&#x2F;    # 库存管理模块<br>└── ui&#x2F;                  # 前端项目</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</sp