><span class=\"line\">274</span><br><span class=\"line\">275</span><br><span class=\"line\">276</span><br><span class=\"line\">277</span><br><span class=\"line\">278</span><br><span class=\"line\">279</span><br><span class=\"line\">280</span><br><span class=\"line\">281</span><br><span class=\"line\">282</span><br><span class=\"line\">283</span><br><span class=\"line\">284</span><br><span class=\"line\">285</span><br><span class=\"line\">286</span><br><span class=\"line\">287</span><br><span class=\"line\">288</span><br><span class=\"line\">289</span><br><span class=\"line\">290</span><br><span class=\"line\">291</span><br><span class=\"line\">292</span><br><span class=\"line\">293</span><br><span class=\"line\">294</span><br><span class=\"line\">295</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 3. 系统功能详解</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 3.1 产品管理模块</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">产品管理模块负责农产品的基础信息管理，包括:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.1.1 产品分类管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 支持多级产品分类</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 可根据分类查询和筛选产品</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 分类数据统计和分析</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.1.2 产品基本信息管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品名称、编码、规格的维护</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品图片和详细描述</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品状态管理（上架、下架）</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.1.3 产品价格管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品价格历史记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 不同区域价格差异管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 价格浮动分析</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.1.4 产品质量标准管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 质量等级定义</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 质量检测标准维护</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 质量检测结果记录</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 3.2 生产管理模块</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">生产管理模块记录农产品从种植到收获的全过程:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.2.1 种植计划管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 年度/季度种植计划制定</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 种植计划执行跟踪</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 种植面积和预计产量管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.2.2 农事活动记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 耕种、播种、施肥、灌溉等活动记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 农事活动时间线展示</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 农事活动成本核算</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.2.3 农药化肥使用记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 农药、化肥使用种类和数量记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 使用时间和负责人记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 安全用药提醒和预警</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.2.4 收获管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 收获时间和产量记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 收获质量等级评定</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 收获成本核算</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.2.5 生产过程追溯</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 全流程生产数据查询</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 二维码/溯源码生成</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 种植环境监测数据集成</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 3.3 库存管理模块</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">库存管理模块负责产品入库、出库管理:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.3.1 入库管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品入库登记</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 入库质量检验</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 入库单据生成和管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.3.2 出库管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 产品出库登记</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 出库审批流程</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 出库单据生成和管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.3.3 库存查询</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 实时库存查询</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 库存变动历史记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 多维度库存分析</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.3.4 库存预警</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 库存不足预警</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 库存积压预警</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 保质期预警</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.3.5 库存盘点</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 定期盘点计划</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 盘点结果记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 盘点差异分析和处理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 3.4 系统管理模块</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">系统管理模块提供基础的系统管理功能:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.1 用户管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 用户信息维护</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 用户状态管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 用户密码策略</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.2 角色管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 角色创建和维护</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 角色权限分配</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 角色用户关联</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.3 菜单管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 系统菜单维护</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 菜单权限设置</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 动态菜单控制</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.4 权限管理</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 功能权限控制</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 数据权限控制</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 权限分配和回收</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.5 系统监控</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 服务器性能监控</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 系统运行状态监控</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 数据库性能监控</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 3.4.6 操作日志</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 用户操作记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 系统异常日志</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 安全审计日志</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 4. 系统使用指南</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 4.1 登录系统</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">1. 访问系统首页</span><br><span class=\"line\">2. 输入用户名和密码，点击&quot;登录&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">3. 填写验证码进行身份验证</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 4.2 产品管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">1. 在左侧菜单选择&quot;产品管理&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">2. 可以进行产品的查询、新增、修改、删除操作</span><br><span class=\"line\">3. 填写完整的产品信息，包括产品名称、分类、规格等</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 4.3 生产管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">1. 在左侧菜单选择&quot;生产管理&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">2. 可以记录农产品生产的各个环节</span><br><span class=\"line\">3. 支持按照时间段和农产品种类进行查询</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 4.4 库存管理</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">1. 在左侧菜单选择&quot;库存管理&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">2. 可以进行入库、出库操作</span><br><span class=\"line\">3. 查看当前库存状态和库存预警信息</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 5. 接口文档</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">系统提供了完整的RESTful API，可通过Swagger文档查看。主要接口包括:</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 5.1 认证接口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/login`: 用户登录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/logout`: 用户注销</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/captchaImage`: 获取验证码</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 5.2 产品管理接口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/product/list`: 获取产品列表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/product/detail/&#123;id&#125;`: 获取产品详情</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/product/add`: 添加产品</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/product/update`: 更新产品</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/product/delete/&#123;id&#125;`: 删除产品</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 5.3 生产管理接口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/produce/plan/list`: 获取生产计划列表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/produce/record/list`: 获取生产记录</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/produce/harvest/list`: 获取收获记录</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 5.4 库存管理接口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/inventory/list`: 获取库存列表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/inventory/in`: 产品入库</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/inventory/out`: 产品出库</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `/inventory/check`: 库存盘点</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 6. 数据库设计</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 6.1 主要数据表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 产品管理相关表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_product`: 产品信息表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_product_category`: 产品分类表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_product_price`: 产品价格表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_product_quality`: 产品质量标准表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 生产管理相关表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_produce_plan`: 生产计划表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_produce_activity`: 农事活动表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_produce_material`: 生产资料使用表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_produce_harvest`: 收获记录表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 库存管理相关表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_inventory`: 库存主表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_inventory_in`: 入库记录表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_inventory_out`: 出库记录表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `ncp_inventory_check`: 库存盘点表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 系统管理相关表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_user`: 用户表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_role`: 角色表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_menu`: 菜单表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_role_menu`: 角色菜单关联表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_user_role`: 用户角色关联表</span><br><span class=\"line\">- `sys_oper_log`: 操作日志表</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 6.2 核心表字段说明</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 产品表(ncp_product)</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 字段名 | 类型 | 描述 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">|-------|------|------|</span><br><span class=\"line\">| product_id | bigint | 产品ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| product_name | varchar(100) | 产品名称 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| product_code | varchar(50) | 产品编码 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| category_id | bigint | 分类ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| specification | varchar(200) | 规格 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| unit | varchar(20) | 单位 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| status | char(1) | 状态(0正常 1停用) |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_by | varchar(64) | 创建者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_time | datetime | 创建时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_by | varchar(64) | 更新者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_time | datetime | 更新时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| remark | varchar(500) | 备注 |</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 生产计划表(ncp_produce_plan)</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 字段名 | 类型 | 描述 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">|-------|------|------|</span><br><span class=\"line\">| plan_id | bigint | 计划ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| plan_name | varchar(100) | 计划名称 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| product_id | bigint | 产品ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| plan_area | decimal(10,2) | 计划面积 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| plan_output | decimal(10,2) | 计划产量 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| start_time | datetime | 开始时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| end_time | datetime | 结束时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| status | char(1) | 状态 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_by | varchar(64) | 创建者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_time | datetime | 创建时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_by | varchar(64) | 更新者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_time | datetime | 更新时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| remark | varchar(500) | 备注 |</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#### 库存表(ncp_inventory)</span><br><span class=\"line\">| 字段名 | 类型 | 描述 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">|-------|------|------|</span><br><span class=\"line\">| inventory_id | bigint | 库存ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| product_id | bigint | 产品ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| warehouse_id | bigint | 仓库ID |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| quantity | decimal(10,2) | 数量 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| unit | varchar(20) | 单位 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| warning_quantity | decimal(10,2) | 预警数量 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| status | char(1) | 状态 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_by | varchar(64) | 创建者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| create_time | datetime | 创建时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_by | varchar(64) | 更新者 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| update_time | datetime | 更新时间 |</span><br><span class=\"line\">| remark | varchar(500) | 备注 |</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 7. 常见问题与解决方案</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 7.1 登录问题</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">**问题**: 无法获取验证码  </span><br><span class=\"line\">**解决**: 检查网络连接，确保后端服务正常运行，清除浏览器缓存</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">**问题**: 密码错误次数过多被锁定  </span><br><span class=\"line\">**解决**: 联系管理员解锁账户或等待锁定时间过期</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 7.2 数据导入导出问题</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">**问题**: 大批量数据导入速度慢  </span><br><span class=\"line\">**解决**: 使用批量导入接口，避免单条导入，或在非高峰期进行导入操作</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">**问题**: 导出数据格式错误  </span><br><span class=\"line\">**解决**: 确认导出文件格式选择正确，检查导出数据的字段映射关系</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">### 7.3 性能优化建议</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- 定期清理不必要的历史数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 建立合理的数据库索引</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 使用缓存减少数据库访问</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 优化查询语句，避免全表扫描</span><br><span class=\"line\">- 前端分页加载大量数据</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">## 8. 系统特色与优势</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">- **全链路追溯**: 实现农产品从种植到销售的全过程追溯</span><br><span class=\"line\">- **数据可视化**: 丰富的图表和报表展示业务数据</span><br><span class=\"line\">- **模块化设计**: 系统模块可独立部署和扩展</span><br><span class=\"line\">- **权限精细控制**: 支持功能权限和数据权限的精细化控制</span><br><span class=\"line\">- **移动端适配**: 支持在移动设备上查看和操作系统</span><br><span class=\"line\">- **智能化提醒**: 库存预警</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">*本文档最后更新时间: 2025年4月18日* </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.2k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"toc":"","data":[]}